  lines:
  - english: Move along
    swedish: Ror pa pakarna
  - english: Greetings
    swedish: Var halsad
  - english: Good day
    swedish: God dag
  - english: How do you do?
    swedish: Allt val
  - english: Good day to you
    swedish: En god dag till dig
  - english: Yes?
    swedish: Na
  - english: Can I help you?
    swedish: Kan jag dig hjalpa
  - english: "G\xE9fru the tanner is asking for sturdy wolf pelts.\nIf you come by
      any, you should to him talk."
    swedish: 'Garvare Gefru soker vargpalsar av gott slag '
  - english: Those cursed wolves...
    swedish: Dessa fargjordade varjar...
  - english: I should be hunting wolf
    swedish: Jag borde jaga varg
  - english: Bandits are lurking in the wild. Be aware.
    swedish: Banditer ruvar i det vilda. Tag dig i akt.
  - english: No dawdling
    swedish: Sta inte har och dra
  - english: Come now
    swedish: Sesa
  - english: What wouldn't I do for a pint
    swedish: Jag skulle ge mycket for en slurk ol just nu
  - english: No idling
    swedish: Slosa inte min tid
  - english: Do not tarry
    swedish: Droj icke
  - english: Any problem?
    swedish: Nagot fel
  - english: All these wolf attacks...
    swedish: Alla dessa varganfall...
  - english: I swear, he was only as tall as my boot!
    swedish: Jag svar, han var hog som min stovel!
  - english: Sad, that about the poor girl...
    swedish: Sorg over den stackars flickan...
